  "html": "<h1>Applies to</h1>\r\n  <ul>\r\n    <li>PCI DSS Requirement 5.2</li>\r\n    <li>PCI DSS Requirement 5.2.a</li>\r\n  </ul>\r\n  <h1>What to Check For</h1>\r\n  <p>The information security policy should require updating of anti-virus software and definitions.</p>\r\n  <h1>Why</h1>\r\n  <p>The anti-virus definitions and anti-virus engine have to be updated frequently to be effective because malware threats evolve rapidly.\r\n</p>\r\n  <h1>How to Check</h1>\r\n  <p>Review the information security policy to make sure that it requires updating of anti-virus software and definitions. Review the anti-virus configuration to make sure it matches the policy requirements.</p>\r\n  <h1>How to Fix</h1>\r\n  <p>Add a point to the information security policy that requires updating of anti-virus software and definitions. Install and configure an anti-virus. Configure the anti-virus to update its engine and definitions. Designate a staff member to be responsible for\r\n maintaining the anti-virus system.</p>\r\n  <h1>Related Items</h1>\r\n  <ul>\r\n    <li>\r\n      <a href=\"/article/6a12327a-3bc3-4acc-af65-9145046280b9\">Deploy an Anti-Virus</a>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li>\r\n      <a href=\"/article/43728505-d3a3-4540-be81-c8bab54e6f6d\">The anti-virus updates itself automatically</a>\r\n    </li>\r\n  </ul>"
